</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/Homestuck" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/Homestuck">Homestuck</a></em>: After Jane nearly gets blown up trying to retrieve the mail, her dad sends her to her room. She is glumly certain she is now "perma-grounded for life."
