</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Website/GoAnimate" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Website/GoAnimate">Go Animate</a></em> became (in)famous on <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Website/YouTube" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Website/YouTube">YouTube</a> for the multiple "X gets grounded" videos made with it. The videos usually end with the parents of whatever character is the protagonist telling them "You are grounded <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OverlyLongGag" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OverlyLongGag">grounded grounded grounded grounded grounded grounded</a> for (overly long number) years! Go to your room!"
